    <section id="get-started" class="get-started section-bg" style="height: 100vh;">
        <div class="container">
  
          <div class="row justify-content-between gy-4">
  
            <div class="col-lg-6 d-flex align-items-center" data-aos="fade-up">
              <div class="content">
                <h3>Login to our system to get save data</h3>
                <p>Join our literary community today and unlock a world of exclusive book reviews, personalized reading recommendations, and a vibrant community of fellow book lovers.
                <p>Register now to start your journey into the depths of literature and discover new favorites, share insights, and engage with stories that move and inspire you. Sign up to explore, connect, and enrich your reading experience with us.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
  
